title: FDOT District 2 -- Medical Faciltiies, Florida, 2006
name: FDOT District 2 -- Medical Faciltiies, Florida, 2006
description: This dataset contains medical facilities and related entities which include: hospitals and nursing facilities; outpatient care centers; medical and diagnostic laboratories; emergency health care centers; medical clinics; nursing homes; physicians; dentists and other practitioners. Eye clinics, ophthalmic specialties and patient laboratories are also included . This is a polygon layer of parts of a parcel or the whole parcel involved with a health related entity. This GIS layer was produced by the North Central Florida Regional Planning Council (NCFRPC) under contract with FDOT District 2 in early 2005, and by the Northeast Florida Regional Planning Council (NEFRPC) under contract with FDOT District 2 in early 2006. This is one of many layers that fall into the general category of "sociocultural" GIS data.
